<div align="center"><h3>AmarokFS Startup Script<br/>

<p><b>About:</b><br/>
This script simply provides a shortcut for starting AmarokFS ("Amarok Full
Screen") from within Amarok itself. If multiple X-Screens exist it can get selected on which it will be started.
</p>
<p>This script is part of the AmarokFS ubuntu packages</p>

<p><b>Usage:</b><br/>
When the script is running, you will have an "AmarokFS" menu entry in your playlist popup menu; now simply select "Run AmarokFS ( on Screen #" to activate AmarokFS on the selected screen
</p>

